                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4117Interpretation">Interpretation and symbolic commentary of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1546Genesi">Genesis</ref>
                      and <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1367Exodus">Exodus</ref>
